nodes.text: This Twi'lek mother and her child were captured as hostages at a Coruscant train station by Cassie Cryar, a thief of the Coruscant underworld, while she was being chased by the Padawan Ahsoka Tano. The Twi'lek was freed when Jedi Master Tera Sinube disarmed Cryar and knocked her unconscious.
